		<h4 class="how__title">Time</h4>
		<div class="how__third">
			<h5 class="how__sub-title">How is time measured?</h5>
			<p class="how__paragraph">
				Time is measured by a set of predetermined intervals. The most basic unit of time is the second.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="how__third">
			<h5 class="how__sub-title">What do we use to measure time?</h5>
			<p class="how__paragraph">
				Many things have been used to measure a second. Kids on the playground often count seconds by saying the word "Mississippi."
				Old clocks used pendulumns to keep time, relying on their stedy oscillation. However, these methods are highly inaccurate
				over time.
			</p>
		</div>
